---
title: DIY Queso and Spiced Chips Serves 2 | with Jalapeños
description: Creamy, cheesy with a hint of jalapeño and a pop of fresh, herby flavour from tomatoes and cilantro. Grab a spiced lime tortilla chip and dig in!
